parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "LwAnEx.A woman of the law, sworn to defend our city from crime...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LwAnEx.... was responsible for propping up the largest criminal organization in our country's history.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LwAnOp.She recruits a woman who escaped from prison!... A woman who still has several years left to serve… A dangerous and unremorseful thief!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LwAnEx.Aided by an officer of the law… 1Hero Canmore… A murderer and a right-hand man to Andrea Kimura’s criminal enterprise.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LwAnDe.With a little luck, these low-lifes would be tarnishing the art world and undermining the science of archeology...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LwAnDe.... under the leadership of a psychotic lunatic… Duncan Helmer.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LwAnEx.Thank God we stopped them when we did…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LwAnDe.And after all this… After decades of deceit… You expect me to simply walk out of this courtroom?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdAnOp^.Another outburst like that and I’ll charge you with contempt.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdMaAg^.I will not stand for such accusations!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LwAnEx.Your glasses literally have golden dollar signs in them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdMaAg^.These are prescription glasses! Remove this man from my courtroom.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdBaEx^.On charges of theft, criminal conspiracy, and corruption, I find the defendant, Andrea Kimura, guilty.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdBaEx^.I hereby order Andrea Kimura to house arrest for a period of one year.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdBaEx^.On the charges of theft and criminal conspiracy, I find the defendant, Nellie Cole, not guilty.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdFrEx^.Miss Cole, you are hereby cleared of your criminal record for your role in taking down the Eclipse Guild kingpin, Duncan Helmer.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnOp.Oh, come on! This is outrageous, Your Honor!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdBaEx^.On the charges of theft and criminal conspiracy, I find the defendant, 1Hero Canmore, not guilty…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdFrEx^.Your dedication to the force is admirable and I hereby promote you to senior detective.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFrOp.I don’t know what to say, Andrea…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.I held up my end of the bargain.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaDe^.I don’t know how you do it, 1Hero… You always find a way to win.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Same to you, Jon. You don’t know how much you’ve helped not just me, but the whole world.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnDe.What’s going on here? How did you pull this off?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlEx^.Calm down, Paul. There’s no story here… I have something far juicier we can discuss later.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.I take it you had something to do with that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFrOp^.I look forward to working with you on the next case, detective.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe.It seems Miss Bhatt and I will be getting a lot closer in the coming months.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.You didn’t hear? Andrea is now Melissa’s neighbor.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.Let’s just say… I downgraded a bit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LaWoOp.Hey, 1Hero, do you know where Ella is?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LaWoCl.Is she okay? Is… she in trouble?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.The investigation into Morgan Deluna is ongoing. We can’t comment any further.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I’m sorry, Larry, I can’t help you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaFlEx^.Come on, Dad. Let’s go get some lunch.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaDe.Seems I’m not the only one who lost her home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx.I think I can get used to condo life… It’s quaint.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiHaOp^.I think this calls for a celebration.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx^.Too bad the mansion is locked up… It would be the perfect place for a party.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.You know… The state owns the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Guess who’s in charge of the keys?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.It’s been inspected and deemed structurally sound… and now it’s for sale!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.I don’t know how I feel about sneaking into that mansion again.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFlEx^.Oh, Mom. Just let loose. It’ll be fine.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe.I have a feeling she’ll show up to the party.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnWoEx.I ain’t going to an orgy dressed like this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl^.Wait… What about Andrea? She’s under house arrest?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.Don’t worry about that. I’ve made arrangements.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Everyone, meet at the mansion in two hours.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ObBaEx.I didn’t know judges could promote police personnel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdBaEx.No need to suck up, detective. Just enjoy your freedom.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Any reason you’re not in your office?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdFlEx.I’m waiting for a phone call to the courtroom phone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdBaDe.Remember, the location needs to be very scenic. Only the best for government housing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdHaEx.Did you know there are Koi fish that cost six figures?... I bet they have magic powers… No… I’m certain they have magic powers.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaWoDe.I hope you find something in the Casula Forest, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Good news! I found the perfect spot for… the state’s government housing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdHaAg^.This looks amazing! I can build a fishing pier and maybe put some nice expensive Japanese koi fish in there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaAnDe.So does this mean my farm is safe… Your Honor?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdAnDe^.We’ll see… Now go back to your country bumpkin life and give that loud voice of yours a rest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Excuse me, Your Honor, but it’s not like the state really needs two mansions.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdBaEx^.Very well, Miss Ray. The court will rescind the state seizure of your land.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdWoCl^.Now if you’ll excuse me, I need to take a long overdue bathroom break.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JdWoCl^.I really need to stop eating spicy tacos.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaAnDe.If it had been left up to that judge, I don’t know what would’ve happened.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.I’m sure you could’ve figured out a way.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFrDe.Seeing as how we’re all alone here, maybe we could tarry a bit…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFlDe.… and see how that would’ve played out?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFlOp.Your Honor, my farm is in danger… Whatever shall I do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Miss Carol Ray, you stand before the court to contest an order of the state. Please state your case.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaWoOp.I’m just a simple country farmer. My farm is everything to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaWoEx.But then I received this order from the court, and…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaSaCl.It says the state is taking my farm away!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.But there’s more to this matter, isn’t there? Something about Casula ruins.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaAnDe.Yes, I recently discovered Casula ruins in a cave on my land.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaWoDe.And now the state is saying it has to preserve them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaWoEx.That’s why they’re taking my land away, Your Honor.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.It’s a very serious matter, Miss Ray. The state has a responsibility to secure the history of the state’s indigenous culture.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaAnOp.So I’m to be left out of hearth and home?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.Order in the court! Miss Ray, you will calm yourself down, or I will hold you in contempt of the court.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.The state has a strong case here. I’m afraid that if you have nothing more to add, I’ll have to rule in favor of the state.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFrEx.As it turns out, I would like to offer up something for the consideration of the court.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFlEx.But it’s very sensitive. May I approach the bench, Your Honor?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Hmm, very well, Miss Ray. I’ll allow it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Damn, you got really serious at the end.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFrEx.I had to make sure I got the outcome I wanted.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFrOp.Don’t worry about me. I’ll head home on my own in a minute.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFlEx.Just admiring your office, 1Hero. It’s quite lovely.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.You might make the judge mad if he finds you hanging around here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Well, if you insist. I’ll see you later, Carol.");
